{"tid":672602,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"珍肝併切雞飯","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T15:29:33.000Z","uid":62277,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0a55eb4aa6084e2e3daff58e8cff47840eb3988d","tid":672602,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"相比起切雞,我更鍾意呢度既雞雜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/143524_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F143524_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ef8f340e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞肝鬆化幼滑,又唔會澀口<br />\n雞腎新鮮爽口<br />\n兩樣都完全無怪味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/144123_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F144123_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b9cb929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切雞比一般冰鮮雞多少少雞味,清香<br />\n口感係類似走地雞,彈性有咬口<br />\n<br />\n該店話自己採用本地活雞,唔知係咪堅<br />\n但佢唔係我喺香港食過最有雞味既雞<br />\n下次會叫佢薑蓉分開上<br />\n睇睇會唔會更食得出雞味"},{"pid":"c417b33a4715453cfb7e27be6bc29b26e68fa629","tid":672602,"uid":3167,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:54:32.000Z","msg":"薑蓉冇蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e700d1387bcd7dd5094d4a73855401e193a92cc6","tid":672602,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"新鮮雞貴到仆街喎賣你幾錢碟？"},{"pid":"ea5b022442e7f060f08214c990c599a3cbb42d67","tid":672602,"uid":48566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"雞雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊到"},{"pid":"f68b049265e8902a505d78460d